1
00:00:28,160 --> 00:00:29,300
The family head is imprisoned.

2
00:00:29,300 --> 00:00:30,330
Madam is detained.

3
00:00:30,330 --> 00:00:33,300
You, Su Yao, brought this disaster of extermination upon us all!

4
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:35,630
Why should the entire Su family be buried with you?

5
00:00:35,630 --> 00:00:36,300
Exactly.

6
00:00:36,900 --> 00:00:39,200
You refused to be a proper young madam of the Imperial Clan.

7
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:39,530
Hmph.

8
00:00:39,830 --> 00:00:43,330
And insisted on throwing yourself at that Lin Fan with his Desolate Holy Body.

9
00:00:43,330 --> 00:00:44,660
Look what happened now.

10
00:00:45,260 --> 00:00:47,200
He was blown to pieces,

11
00:00:47,860 --> 00:00:50,660
and now we're going to be massacred because of you.

12
00:00:53,460 --> 00:00:54,520
What did I do wrong?

13
00:00:54,730 --> 00:00:57,200
I just wanted to pursue true love and freedom!

14
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,960
It's obviously that demon Gu Linyuan using his power to bully others.

15
00:00:59,960 --> 00:01:01,360
Slaughtering the innocent.

16
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:02,760
Why are you blaming me?

17
00:01:03,430 --> 00:01:04,560
Who dares touch her?

18
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:06,660
You?

19
00:01:07,500 --> 00:01:09,360
You're Chu Feng from the stables.

20
00:01:10,660 --> 00:01:12,400
Come back to the Su family and feed the horses with me.

21
00:01:12,400 --> 00:01:13,860
At least you won't starve to death.

22
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:15,060
Don't be afraid, Yao'er.

23
00:01:15,060 --> 00:01:15,789
With me here,

24
00:01:16,330 --> 00:01:17,390
no one can hurt you.

25
00:01:19,230 --> 00:01:20,460
Look who it is.

26
00:01:20,800 --> 00:01:22,660
Just a stinky stable boy.

27
00:01:22,700 --> 00:01:24,600
Do you think you're worthy to play the hero here?

28
00:01:24,600 --> 00:01:26,730
A stable boy dares to meddle in the Su family's affairs?

29
00:01:26,730 --> 00:01:27,500
You must have a death wish.

30
00:01:27,500 --> 00:01:29,000
I've endured for a long time,

31
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,560
just to protect you.

32
00:01:31,760 --> 00:01:33,630
Since the Su family cannot accommodate you,

33
00:01:33,630 --> 00:01:34,759
then I, the War King,

34
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,330
will hold up the sky for you.

35
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:38,259
The War King's decree is issued.

36
00:01:38,259 --> 00:01:40,720
Where are my hundred thousand loyal troops?

37
00:01:41,930 --> 00:01:42,800
It's the War King's decree!

38
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,060
Our Lord has returned!

39
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:47,100
Sell all our properties,

40
00:01:47,200 --> 00:01:48,700
assemble the Shadow Iron Cavalry,

41
00:01:48,700 --> 00:01:50,700
and come with me to welcome our Lord!

42
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:55,030
I await your command, my Lord.

43
00:01:58,430 --> 00:01:59,130
Yao'er.

44
00:01:59,660 --> 00:02:01,920
This divine water can create all things.

45
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,860
I will now restore your sight.

46
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,800
I... I can see!

47
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:12,700
There's no need to fear, Yao'er.

48
00:02:12,930 --> 00:02:14,530
Although Gu Linyuan is a Quasi-Emperor,

49
00:02:14,530 --> 00:02:16,160
I too once reached that realm.

50
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,200
Though my vitality is depleted now,

51
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:18,560
and I have fallen to the Great Sage realm,

52
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,700
as long as I gather my old troops,

53
00:02:19,700 --> 00:02:20,530
assemble the battle array,

54
00:02:20,530 --> 00:02:21,790
I might not lose to him.

55
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,700
I will surely rescue your parents

56
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,100
and seek justice for you.

57
00:02:25,130 --> 00:02:25,860
Chu Feng,

58
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:29,160
just because of a steamed bun I gave you back then,

59
00:02:29,560 --> 00:02:32,000
you are willing to wage war against the Imperial Clan for me?

60
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,630
No.

61
00:02:33,160 --> 00:02:33,900
Because...

62
00:02:35,329 --> 00:02:36,160
you are her.

63
00:02:36,760 --> 00:02:38,630
The Imperial Gu family has announced joyous news.

64
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:40,900
The family head, Gu Linyuan, is about to take a concubine.

65
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:42,760
The bride is Lu Wanqing, wife of the Su family head.

66
00:02:42,760 --> 00:02:43,829
Lu Wanqing?

67
00:02:44,100 --> 00:02:46,460
Gu Linyuan has always acted tyrannically.

68
00:02:46,460 --> 00:02:47,700
Doing whatever he pleases.

69
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,430
Snatching someone else's wife

70
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,800
quite suits his demonic style.

71
00:02:52,030 --> 00:02:54,560
I heard long ago that Su Changkong's wife is exceptionally beautiful.

72
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,760
Her figure and looks are like the Profound Girl of the Nine Heavens descending.

73
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,300
So the rumors were actually true.

74
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:00,430
No wonder even a Quasi-Emperor couldn't resist her.

75
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:01,430
Me too!

76
00:03:01,730 --> 00:03:04,460
The Gu family head is truly a role model for us all!

77
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:05,600
This preference of Mengde,

78
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:06,800
the legacy of Emperor Wu of Wei,

79
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,460
truly wins my heart!

80
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,320
Why is it so noisy outside?

81
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:19,930
Did Father change his mind

82
00:03:20,600 --> 00:03:21,930
and decide to propose to Yao'er

83
00:03:21,930 --> 00:03:23,030
on my behalf again?

84
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:24,500
Young Master.

85
00:03:24,760 --> 00:03:26,020
It's not your wedding.

86
00:03:26,160 --> 00:03:27,500
The Master

87
00:03:27,660 --> 00:03:29,130
is announcing to the world today

88
00:03:29,130 --> 00:03:30,990
that he is taking a Dao companion.

89
00:03:32,730 --> 00:03:34,060
As a quasi-emperor,

90
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,329
it's normal for Father

91
00:03:35,329 --> 00:03:36,800
to seek a dual cultivation partner.

92
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,200
Which Holy Land's saintess is it?

93
00:03:38,200 --> 00:03:38,660
It's...

94
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:41,860
It's the companion Su Changkong abandoned,

95
00:03:41,860 --> 00:03:42,530
Lu Wanqing.

96
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:43,660
Which means

97
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:45,260
she is Miss Su Yao's...

98
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:45,900
Dad!

99
00:03:45,900 --> 00:03:47,230
I love Su Yao so much,

100
00:03:47,329 --> 00:03:49,260
and you took her mother as your Dao companion!

101
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:51,260
What should I call Su Yao from now on?

102
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,300
No!

103
00:03:56,730 --> 00:03:57,560
My lords.

104
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:58,730
Is

105
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:00,860
Master Gu letting me go?

106
00:04:01,530 --> 00:04:02,530
Let you go?

107
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,530
Today is the dual cultivation ceremony

108
00:04:04,530 --> 00:04:06,260
for Fairy Lu and our Master.

109
00:04:06,760 --> 00:04:08,500
The Master is merciful.

110
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:11,800
He said that since Fairy Lu has attained the Great Dao,

111
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:13,630
it wouldn't make sense for you, the one who abandoned her,

112
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:15,690
not to come and witness the ceremony.

113
00:04:17,829 --> 00:04:18,630
Let's go.

114
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,560
Go get some immortal aura.

115
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:23,060
This is purely cruel.

116
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,400
Gu Linyuan,

117
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:27,360
you're too cruel!

118
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,560
Yes.

119
00:04:30,760 --> 00:04:32,760
Thank you for your mercy, Master Gu.

120
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:33,960
I, the sinner,

121
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:34,960
will go

122
00:04:35,530 --> 00:04:36,860
to attend the ceremony.

123
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:43,630
Greetings, Battle King.

124
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,630
Old subordinates, hear my command!

125
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:51,430
Follow me to the Imperial Clan to stop the wedding!

126
00:04:54,100 --> 00:04:58,630
Yaochi Holy Land gifts a pair of ten-thousand-year Sea-Calming Pearls

127
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:01,960
to congratulate Master Gu on his wedding!

128
00:05:02,500 --> 00:05:06,760
Ziwei Holy Land gifts three top-grade Holy Spirit Veins!
